         <text>Process Tower: Procure To Pay
Process Group: Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-110-060A Receive Product From Subcontractor
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-CB88EAA1-0080-407D-B656-CE2C05BC09ED" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
